title: Kennedy.2015.08.17.WS.SDTV.x264-XAiO
description:
"Kennedy" is a news panel show hosted by Kennedy Montgomery. Kennedy Montgomery is a libertarian that you may recognize from 90's MTV, Stossel, and the Independents.

_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2_,-'2

Kennedy kicks the night off talking about the recent debates and the shakeup they've caused within the GOP field.

Tonight we're joined by GAVIN MCCINES, DAVE SMITH, and JULIE ROGINSKY. They continue to discuss the GOP's surging underdogs. Somehow a fiery debate about immigration comes out of it. Good stuff.

Our pugnacious panel returns to talk about Hillary's rapidly escalating email scandal.

Charlie LeDuff is here via satellite to talk about his show "The Americans with Charlie LeDuff" and Donald Trump. Mostly Donald Trump. (He tried to turn in a resume for Vice President.)

The panel returns to talk about a potential Fresh Prince reboot. Are the 90's coming back? Some guy sends back feel good participation trophy his kid had "earned".

RYAN MAURO is here to argue against the Iran deal. Kennedy is kind of for it.

Nightcap: An interview on Nightcap? WYATT SCOTT (Canadian) is here via satellite to talk about his badass political ad where he rides a goose, slays a dragon, and melts a robot with his irresistible laser eyes.
